videos.description: Theo Pinson spins around a defender on his way to a throwdown dunk for North Carolina.
videos.headline: Pinson spins to the basket for dunk

videos.description: Cameron Johnson spins around defenders on the fast break and passes ahead to Joel Berry II who lays it in.
videos.headline: UNC fast break leads to layup

videos.description: After the ball is knocked loose, Sterling Manley makes the two-handed putback dunk off a Joel Berry II miss.
videos.headline: Fight for loose ball sets up UNC putback dunk

videos.description: Theo Pinson passes to Sterling Manley underneath the basket, who makes a big two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Manley dunks off cross-court pass

videos.description: Luke Maye passes over to Joel Berry II in the corner who hits the 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Berry II knocks down corner 3-pointer

videos.description: Jalek Felton picks off the pass from Georgia Tech and takes it all the way for the one-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Felton slams off fast-break steal

videos.description: Theo Pinson throws deep down the court to Joel Berry II who hits the layup.
videos.headline: Berry II lays it in on leak-out score
